column5: just as much luck predicting weather with a Dart Board  Ill believe it when i see it and rejoice because I havent seen it in a very long time

Any one ever heard of that story from Al Gore....oh what was it now? Oh yeah that tale about global warming. We all remember him right? The guy that cries cutting back and strikes fear into our children of gloom and doom while he and his family enjoy the comfort of having a $4000.00 per month utility bill.  Hmmm a freezing winter will help the naysayers of that theory to say "See I told you so."  Me I don't side with either platform on that subject, I just like to observe, laugh and say oh what ever you want to believe and shoot my mouth off. That's only, can I say it? Please  just my 2 cents worth.
